{"tid":795552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［又話唔知？］方濟各結束愛爾蘭訪問　拒回應涉包庇麥卡里克性侵","createTime":"2018-08-27T06:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T09:43:35.000Z","uid":24284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe95313627cc5d1ddaf43009d0e6478740b76c36","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"天主教教宗方濟各周日（26日）結束2天訪問愛爾蘭行程。他臨離開前被問到，前梵蒂岡駐美國大使指控他早在2013年已知道華盛頓教區前總主教麥卡里克（Theodore McCarrick）捲入腐敗指控，並有包庇之嫌，方濟各拒絕確認或否認指控，表明不會評論。<br />\n教宗方濟各結束愛爾蘭訪問前，最後一個活動是到都柏林鳳凰公園主持彌撒，他在儀式上請求民眾的寬恕，希望他們原諒教會領袖在愛爾蘭所犯的「侵犯、濫用權力及良心及性侵。」<br />\n<br />\n他訪問愛爾蘭期間，曾任梵蒂岡駐美國大使的領銜總主教維加諾（Carlo Maria Vigano）致函保守的天主教媒體《全美天主教紀錄》（National Catholic Register）「爆料」。他在長達11頁的信中自稱2013年6月已告訴方濟各，麥卡里克面對眾多有關他「敗壞」（corrupted）修生及神父的指控，卻到2018年7月28日才接受他呈辭。周日飛往羅馬時，方濟各在飛機接受記者提問，談及這11頁「控書」。他表示信中部分內容就像對自己及盟友的同性戀攻擊一樣，並指事情會「不言自明」，因此不會評論。<br />\n<br />\n方濟各又補充，自己已經讀過信件，相信記者能自行判斷。「這是一種信任行為，我一句話都不會說。」<br />\n<br />\n麥卡里克總主教是近年第一名因相關罪行而辭職的樞機，之後陸續有更多人出來指控麥卡里克曾侵犯他們。而麥卡里克表示對50年前的事已無記憶，也不去評論其他指控了。<br />\n<br />\n十戒：「不可作假見證害人。」"},{"pid":"a27ae24745ef0f10266c8746d3620d97fd766b01","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"方濟各被指放生教會之狼<br />\n<br />\n教宗承受的壓力愈來愈大，周六有一名曾為梵蒂岡效力的高級人員指出，方濟各早在5年已知美國一名「傑出的」樞機主教涉性侵罪行，卻在2018年7月28日接受他呈辭。如果這是事實，教宗也有包庇性罪犯之嫌。梵蒂岡周日未就有關消息回應。<br />\n<br />\n曾任教廷傳播秘書處長的維加諾大主教（Carlo Maria Vigano）在教宗訪愛爾蘭期間，致函保守的天主教媒體《全美天主教紀錄》（National Catholic Register）「爆料」。他在長達11頁的信中自稱2013年6月已告訴方濟各，麥卡里克樞機（Theodore McCarrick）面對眾多有關他性侵低階修士以及神父的指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/227604/教廷前高層籲教宗辭職-方濟各5年前已知性侵者惡行\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F227604%2F%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E5%89%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E7%B1%B2%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7-%E6%96%B9%E6%BF%9F%E5%90%845%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E8%80%85%E6%83%A1%E8%A1%8C&d=bosjxc%2FYLRYutzA32S3YvTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7a63e9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/227604/教廷前高層籲教宗辭職-方濟各5年前已知性侵者惡行</a>"},{"pid":"1201b7f95c0b758e6dd3fd067c6fc7a6ba52db57","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4403048d3331ae0a6c62694a9d6bf7862c4088f","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc05b04b0bbf5ef61274826291a7f36606b33bd3","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55744e1f6f409d2c10e9ea93f3c41b3dcd1db13d","tid":795552,"uid":75406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"回帶<br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2018/08/blog-post_27.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F08%2Fblog-post_27.html%3Fm%3D1&d=bosjxc%2FYLRYutzA32S3YvTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=345f48fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2018/08/blog-post_27.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"aa31aa8556c462e22cbc8dcfcc4f42287733580d","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d13b277a92b5b2c5abe85e8fa6dd5e85e7bfbb","tid":795552,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f689c6f5587b54b63e9b3c47954bebb5f17227","tid":795552,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"「這是一種信任行為，我一句話都不會說。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔敢否認，驚犯十戒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}